item.title: CVE-2022-47556|2024-08-03T14:55:08.319Z -- ormazabal -- ekorrci
item.description: Uncontrolled resource consumption in ekorRCI, allowing an attacker with low-privileged access to the web server to send continuous legitimate web requests to a functionality that is not properly validated, in order to cause a denial of service (DoS) on the device.
